org.openimaj.util.list

Class AbstractFileBackedList<T extends Readable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<T>
        • org.openimaj.util.list.AbstractFileBackedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of readable item held in array
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, RandomisableList<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileLocalFeatureList, FileTwitterStatusList

    public abstract class AbstractFileBackedList<T extends Readable>
extends AbstractList<T>
implements RandomisableList<T>, Cloneable
    A (currently) read-only list that iterates over a file. Both ascii and binary files are supported. Binary files are required to have fixed length records.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare
